io.openems.edge.bridge.modbus.api.task

Interface ReadTask

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ManagedTask, Task
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractReadDigitalInputsTask, AbstractReadInputRegistersTask, AbstractReadTask, FC1ReadCoilsTask, FC2ReadInputsTask, FC3ReadRegistersTask, FC4ReadInputRegistersTask

    public interface ReadTask
extends Task, ManagedTask
    A Modbus 'ReadTask' is holding references to one or more Modbus AbstractModbusElement which have register addresses in the same range. The ReadTask handles the execution (query) on this range. @{link WriteTask} inherits from ReadTask.
